---
title: DeliverAssist Architecture
---
graph TB
    subgraph User["👤 Delivery Worker (Phone/Laptop)"]
        MIC["🎙 Microphone<br/>PCM 16kHz"]
        CAM["📷 Camera<br/>JPEG frames"]
        UI["📱 Browser UI<br/>HTML/JS"]
        SPEAK["🔊 Speaker<br/>Audio playback"]
    end

    subgraph CloudRun["☁️ Google Cloud Run"]
        WS["WebSocket Proxy<br/>(FastAPI)"]
        SP["System Prompt<br/>Worker Rights KB<br/>+ DCWP Data"]
        TH["Tool Handler<br/>Pay Calculator"]
    end

    subgraph Gemini["🤖 Gemini 2.5 Flash Native Audio"]
        LIVE["Live API<br/>Bidi Streaming"]
        LANG["Language Detection<br/>70+ languages"]
        VISION["Image Understanding<br/>Pay Stub OCR"]
        FC["Function Calling<br/>Pay Compliance Check"]
    end

    subgraph Data["📊 NYC Open Data (DCWP)"]
        SURVEY["Worker Survey<br/>7,956 responses"]
        QUARTERLY["Quarterly Tables<br/>Platform earnings"]
        RIGHTS["Worker Rights<br/>NYC Admin Code §20-1522"]
    end

    MIC -->|audio stream| WS
    CAM -->|JPEG| WS
    WS <-->|bidi audio + tool calls| LIVE
    LIVE --> LANG
    LIVE --> VISION
    LIVE --> FC
    FC -->|invoke| TH
    TH -->|result| FC
    SP -.->|injected at session start| LIVE
    Data -.->|loaded into prompt| SP
    LIVE -->|audio response| WS
    WS -->|audio| SPEAK
    WS -->|transcripts| UI
